  "short_description": "A dungeon known as the Abyss has suddenly appeared. To open the \"Door of Darkness\" at its deepest point, the Seeker plunges into the dungeon gate... in search of the truth. Survive the onslaught of dark forces in this twin-stick survival shooter! — Are You Ready to Face Your Destiny?",
