  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『ABYSS SEEKER』 is a twin-stick survivor shooter game where you control your character freely using two sticks, survive waves of enemies within a time limit, and defeat the boss that appears in the final wave to progress to the next dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The shots fired by the player character can be customized by combining items that appear during level-ups, allowing you to alter their properties and fight with your \"unique shot.\" Defeat the relentless forces of darkness and make it out alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※This work is a spin-off based on \"HEAVEN SEEKER ――The Savior of This Cruel World.\" It can be enjoyed as a standalone title.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Stronger Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Area bosses resembling those that appeared in the Sky Castle have been influenced by the Abyss, becoming more powerful and attacking anyone who dares to enter the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge the barrage of bullets unleashed by the boss and take them down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>◆Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, Pentagaia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a castle in the sky where secrets are said to sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lords of the five kingdoms, who have come from the five worlds to the</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >from the five worlds to the Castle in the Sky, wishing to return to their original worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lords of the five kingdoms who have moved from the five worlds to the Celestial Castle in hopes of returning to their original worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The \"sixth seeker\" suddenly appears in the castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the same time, a mysterious dungeon gate also appeared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has lost her memory, and all she remembers is that she has to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is that she must go to the abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the underground gate,         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and then through the Abyss to reach the Abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thus began her journey through the Abyss.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『ABYSS SEEKER』 is a twin-stick survivor shooter game where you control your character freely using two sticks, survive waves of enemies within a time limit, and defeat the boss that appears in the final wave to progress to the next dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The shots fired by the player character can be customized by combining items that appear during level-ups, allowing you to alter their properties and fight with your \"unique shot.\" Defeat the relentless forces of darkness and make it out alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_pa